\appendix
\section{Results with the SSVHEM selection}
\label{app:ssvhem}
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
For completeness we report in this Appendix the results of the
analysis when events are selected requiring at least one jet tagged by
the SSVHEM discriminant.
The coefficients used in Equations~\ref{eq:xsec_llb}
  and~\ref{eq:xsec_llj} are shown in
  Table~\ref{tab:coeff_particle_ssvhem}, results are shown in
  Table~\ref{tab:results_ssvhem}. 
The results obtained are compatible with those derived using the
SSVHPT selection.

